    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      54.0,
      597.37,
      412.87,
      608.41
    ],
    "text": "consideration should be taken into account regarding the above subject matter;",
    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      621.97,
      511.06,
      635.77
    ],
    "text": "The above road was designated a national highway by Gazette no. 561/5 dated 06.06.1989.",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "FootlightMTLight",
      "SymbolMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      641.29,
      544.09,
      655.09
    ],
    "text": "The Minister had not specified a building limit for the Kandy Mahiyangana Padiyathalawa road under",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "FootlightMTLight",
      "SymbolMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      661.48,
      544.01,
      672.52
    ],
    "text": "section 42(1) of the Thoroughfares Act. Therefore, the default building limit set out in section",
    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      678.88,
      546.82,
      689.92
    ],
    "text": "42(2)(a) 15 meters (15 M) from the centre of the roadway is to be considered as the building limit.",
    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      695.44,
      543.83,
      709.24
    ],
    "text": "Therefore, any construction within a 15M from the centre of the highway of the impugned road is",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "FootlightMTLight",
      "SymbolMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      715.72,
      285.41,
      726.76
    ],
    "text": "an illegal construction pursuant to the Act.",
    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      54.0,
      741.04,
      544.19,
      752.08
    ],
    "text": "Section 45(3) of the National Thoroughfares Act No. 40 of 2008 (hereinafter referred to as the Act) stipulates",
    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
